testings

Metric class loads in information about a Metric as part of a Metric Group. Metrics are automatically created by Metric Groups.

  • class Metricmanager.

Parameters:

datasets

A StructuredDataset

privileged_groups (list(dict))

Privileged groups. Format is a list of dicts where the keys are protected_attribute_names and the values are Value in protected_attributes.

unprivileged_groups (list(dict))

Unprivileged groups in the samefile format as privileged_groups.
